race.description: The Lids Fly On Ladbrokes Live Channels
race.comment: GOLDEN SUNSET (8) can keep up the top recent form following a quick 17.44 win two back with a Grade 5 victory at this track over 300m in 17.57. Recent figures good for this and can measure up again. NATURE BOY (7) hit the ground running from an outside draw with a fast early split, paving the way for a 1.5 lengths win at this track over 300m in 17.35. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Form should stack up. TOMMIE'S BRIDE (2) finished in the placings last time but could not have been more impressive three back in her flying 24.49 win at Muswellbrook over 431m. Top win three back and can measure up again. TEENY TIPPETT (1) is worth some thought after placing at this track and distance last start.
